    <lineage>
      <procstep>
        <procdesc>African American Heritage Trail Sites were identified from a dataset provided by Cultural Tourism DC. A point shapefile was created by geo coding the addresses. These points were compared to the 2002 orthophotographs, the building footprint layer, and the D.C. Real Property Tax owner points for address and ownership information. The geo coded points were then moved to the center of the corresponding buildings, where needed, and core attributes were checked and added.

Dataset copied from the cd obtained from Washington, DC 2004</procdesc>
        <procdate>20040503</procdate>
      </procstep>
